{"id": "1515234574156824646", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "type": 19, "author_id": "1424954154656464936", "author_name": "oatstemp", "author_bot": false, "content": "Not really. Uvhash does not synergize well with gmurphy. \nHe can work but it wont be pretty.\n\nGmurphy converts ACTIVE damage to sacrifice stacks.\n\nUvhash's ult and a certain skill  are PASSIVE damage. \n\nThe 4 cost skill is active damage but it needs some time to scale plus, it is rng. \n\n His last skill deals peanuts as damage and exists to chip away barriers and get energy.", "timestamp": "2026-06-13T06:01:14.176000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1240202196658946120"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1515216304595009546", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
